# Wilhelms-Gymnasium Stuttgart — My School Projects

This repository contains academic materials, GFS presentations, and mandatory informatics assignments completed during my time at Wilhelms-Gymnasium Stuttgart.

## 🔗 Quick Links

* **Scratch Profile:** [@TelegramBaum](https://scratch.mit.edu/users/TelegramBaum/)
* **Scratch Class Space:** [Class 2045397](https://scratch.mit.edu/classes/2045397/)

## 📂 Repository Structure

* `Informatics/` — Technical tasks, etc.
    * `scratch/` — Mandatory visual programming assignments.
        * `Fliehippo/` — School tasks (Fliehippo scratch basics with mandatory naming patterns).
        * `runaway from tencent.sb3` — Just some random thing.

